[00:01.353]Lesson 49 | 第49课
[00:04.143]Do you want any meat today, Mrs. Bird? | 伯德太太，你今天想要些肉吗？
[00:06.913]Yes, please. | 是的，请给我来点。
[00:08.993]Do you want beef or lamb? | 你想要牛肉还是羊肉？
[00:11.753]Beef, please. | 牛肉，谢谢。
[00:13.903]This lamb's very good. | 这羊肉很好。
[00:16.103]I like lamb, but my husband doesn't. | 我喜欢羊肉，但我丈夫不喜欢。
[00:20.673]What about some steak? | 来点牛排怎么样？
[00:23.013]This is a nice piece. | 这是块不错的肉。
[00:25.213]Give me that piece, please. | 请把那块肉给我。
[00:28.983]And a pound of mince too. | 再来一磅肉馅。
[00:32.183]Do you want a chicken, Mrs. Bird? They're very nice. | 伯德太太，你想要一只鸡吗？它们很好。
[00:36.143]No, thank you. | 不，谢谢你。
[00:38.863]My husband likes steak, but he doesn't like chicken. | 我丈夫喜欢牛排，但他不喜欢鸡肉。
[00:44.603]To tell you the truth, Mrs. Bird, I don't like chicken either. | 说实话，伯德太太，我也不喜欢鸡肉。